  <brief_title>A Trial Evaluating the Effects of Zoledronic Acid 5 mg Infusion on Bone Mineral Density (BMD) in Postmenopausal Osteoporosis (PMO) Patients Between the Ages of 50 and 65 Years</brief_title>
  <official_title>A One Year, Local, Open Label, Multicentre Trial Evaluating the Effects of Zoledronic Acid 5 mg Infusion on BMD and Biochemical Markers of Bone in PMO Pts Between the Ages of 50 and 65 Years</official_title>
